Introduction

Park Junhee, formerly known as Jun, is a South Korean singer under Beat Interactive. He is the leader of the boy group A.C.E.

Park Junhee appeared on episode seven of I Can See Your Voice 5. He was known as Suncheon's Kangta and was eliminated in the second round.

In 2017, Park Junhee, along with fellow group member Chan, became a contestant on KBS 2TV's idol rebooting show The Unit. He was eliminated in the episode 4 after achieving 27th place.
